    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>RIZZO-Mary L. Died June 30, 2000, at age 97. Beloved wife of the late Jerry G. Rizzo. Beloved aunt of 17 nieces and nephews. Reposing at Pelham Funeral Home, 64 Lincoln Ave, Pelham, NY. Visiting hours Sunday 2-4 and 7-9 PM. Service Monday, July 3, at 10 AM, Christ the Redeemer Church, 1415 Pelhamdale Ave, Pelham Manor, NY.</p>
      </block>
